title: Coldplay & Kylie Minogue - Lhuna (New Single)
description:
Here's Coldplay's new song featuring Kylie Minogue: Lhuna.
The track is very rarely available at the moment so I streamed, recorded it and created an MP3.
It's not in extremely high Audio-quality, but for now it's fair in my opinion.
You can add this one to the EP Prospekts March as an extended track.

Anyway, enjoy the track!

Edit: Whoops, that's now new the track is.
The track is called Lhuna instead of Luhna, for if you may want to have the correct name added into your MP3.
